November 16, 2020 / Much of the case against Jeff Titus is based on the missing shotgun he claimed to have found in the game area. The police say they searched the area and didn't find it — so how was Titus able to locate it, when they had not?

Episode scoring music by Animal Weapon and Blue Dot Sessions.
